{"word":"G3051 - λόγιον - lógion - log'-ee-on - Oracle","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λόγιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">lógion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">log'-ee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Oracle</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வாக்கு - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"a little word, a brief utterance"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of <a href=\"#/G3052 - λόγιος - lógios - log'-ee-os/3052\">G3052</a>; an <i>utterance</i> (of God): - oracle.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1586/1586\">G1586</a>, <a href=\"#/G1588/1588\">G1588</a>, <a href=\"#/G1589/1589\">G1589</a>, <a href=\"#/G249/249\">G249</a>, <a href=\"#/G2980/2980\">G2980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3004/3004\">G3004</a>, <a href=\"#/G3050/3050\">G3050</a>, <a href=\"#/G3051/3051\">G3051</a>, <a href=\"#/G3052/3052\">G3052</a>, <a href=\"#/G3054/3054\">G3054</a>, <a href=\"#/G3055/3055\">G3055</a>, <a href=\"#/G3056/3056\">G3056</a>"}]}